# Google GPU Colab Integration

File: GoogleGPUcolab.md

## Purpose

This document specifies how to integrate **Google Colab GPU processing** into the existing video pipeline.

The goal is to offload heavy LLM tasks to Google Colab while keeping the main system local.

Tasks executed in Colab:

* transcript summarization
* transcript classification
* optional embeddings generation

Tasks executed locally:

* video downloading
* subtitle extraction
* transcript chunking
* SQLite database storage
* search engine
* RAG answering system

LLM models used:

Worker model:
Qwen3.5-4B

Thinker model:
Qwen3.5-9B (local RAG only)

